<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p data-changed="false" data-paragraphid="3">Youth are invaluable to the future of our society, and we believe each and every one of them deserves to grow up in a healthy environment regardless of their upbringing. EJI actively takes part in fund-raising events and activities held by organisations with the same vision.</p>'=>'<p data-changed="false" data-paragraphid="3">青年對我們社會的未來來說是無價的，我們相信他們每個人都應該在一個健康的環境中成長，無論他們的成長經歷如何。EJI 積极參與籌款活動以及由具有相同願景的組織舉辦的活動。 </p>','<p>As one of Hong Kong\'s leading fine jewellery manufacturers, we have been creating dazzling designs that are rooted in quality, integrity and elegance since 1991.</p><h2>SUPPLY CHAIN</h2><p>Elegance Jewellery International Limited (EJI) is a member of the <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Responsible Jewellery Council</a> (RJC), the world\'s leading standard setting organisation for the jewellery and watch industry. As a committed RJC member, the business practices of our entire business operations, including jewellery supply chain are adhered to the latest <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/standards/code-of-practices-2019/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RJC Code of Practices</a>, which provides a common standard for social, ethical, human rights and environmental business practices. EJI is dedicated to creating a healthy work environment and ethical jewellery products, and we strongly encourage all of our business partners to implement the common standard across their operations.</p><p>The Responsible Jewellery Council Policy covers:</p><ul><li>Responsible Supply Chain and Human Rights, from mine to retail</li><li>Labour Rights and Working Conditions</li><li>Health, Safety and Environment</li><li>Gold, Silver, PGM, Diamond and Coloured Gemstone Products</li><li>Anti-Bribery and Corruptions</li></ul><p> </p><p>Click to view:<br /><a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/">EJI RJC Certificate</a><br /><a style="font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px;" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IpdkT6Kq071xcWTR6F2DQAksRk3pU-4E/view?usp=drive_link">EJI RJC Annual Report 2024</a></p>'=>'<p>作為香港領先的高級珠寶製造商之一，自 1991 年以來，我們一直以質量、誠信和優雅為根基，創造令人眼花繚亂的設計。</p><h2>供應鏈</h2><p>優雅珠寶國際有限公司 （EJI） 是 <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">責任珠寶業委員會</a> （RJC） 的成員，該委員會是世界領先的珠寶和鍾錶行業標準制定組織。作為責任珠寶業委員會 （RJC） 的忠實成員，我們整個業務運營的商業實踐，包括珠寶供應鏈，都遵守最新的 <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/standards/code-of-practices-2019/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">責任珠寶業委員會行為準則</a>，該準則為社會、道德、人權和環境商業實踐提供了通用標準。EJI 致力於創造健康的工作環境和合乎道德的珠寶產品，我們強烈鼓勵所有業務合作夥伴在其運營中實施通用標準。  </p><p>責任珠寶業委員會的政策涵蓋：</p><ul><li>負責任的供應鏈和人權，從採礦到零售</li><li>勞工權利和工作條件</li><li>健康、安全與環境</li><li>黃金、白銀、鉑族金屬、鑽石和有色寶石產品</li><li>反賄賂和反腐敗</li></ul><p> </p><p>點擊檢視：<br><a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/">EJI RJC 證書</a><br><a style="font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px;" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IpdkT6Kq071xcWTR6F2DQAksRk3pU-4E/view?usp=drive_link">EJI RJC 2024 年年度報告</a></p>','<p>Since 2010, EJI has gained several Hong Kong business and employer awards, including the Best SME Award, Partner Employer Award, Caring Company Award, and many more.</p>'=>'<p>自 2010 年以來，EJI 已獲得多個香港商業和雇主獎項，包括最佳中小企業獎、合作夥伴雇主獎、商界展關懷獎等。</p>','COMMUNITY'=>'社區','Learn more'=>'瞭解更多資訊','Responsible Employer'=>'負責任的雇主','WE ARE A MEMBER OF'=>'我們是','Youth Philanthropy'=>'青年慈善事業','editor-text-editor-d572eb8'=>'<p>作為香港領先的高級珠寶製造商之一，自 1991 年以來，我們一直以質量、誠信和優雅為根基，創造令人眼花繚亂的設計。</p><h2>供應鏈</h2><p>優雅珠寶國際有限公司 （EJI） 是 <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">責任珠寶業委員會</a> （RJC） 的成員，該委員會是世界領先的珠寶和鍾錶行業標準制定組織。作為責任珠寶業委員會 （RJC） 的忠實成員，我們整個業務運營的商業實踐，包括珠寶供應鏈，都遵守最新的 <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/standards/code-of-practices-2019/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">責任珠寶業委員會行為準則</a>，該準則為社會、道德、人權和環境商業實踐提供了通用標準。EJI 致力於創造健康的工作環境和合乎道德的珠寶產品，我們強烈鼓勵所有業務合作夥伴在其運營中實施通用標準。  </p><p>責任珠寶業委員會的政策涵蓋：</p><ul><li>負責任的供應鏈和人權，從採礦到零售</li><li>勞工權利和工作條件</li><li>健康、安全與環境</li><li>黃金、白銀、鉑族金屬、鑽石和有色寶石產品</li><li>反賄賂和反腐敗</li></ul><p> </p><p>點擊檢視：<br><a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/">EJI RJC 證書</a><br><a style="font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px;" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IpdkT6Kq071xcWTR6F2DQAksRk3pU-4E/view?usp=drive_link">EJI RJC 2024 年年度報告</a></p>','editor-text-editor-e469b54'=>'<p data-changed="false" data-paragraphid="3">青年對我們社會的未來來說是無價的，我們相信他們每個人都應該在一個健康的環境中成長，無論他們的成長經歷如何。EJI 積极參與籌款活動以及由具有相同願景的組織舉辦的活動。 </p>','editor-text-editor-f6794b3'=>'<p>自 2010 年以來，EJI 已獲得多個香港商業和雇主獎項，包括最佳中小企業獎、合作夥伴雇主獎、商界展關懷獎等。</p>','https://h3y8j2unfg-staging.onrocket.site/tag/corporate-social-responsibility/'=>'https://h3y8j2unfg-staging.onrocket.site/zh-hant/tag/%e4%bc%81%e6%a5%ad%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e8%b2%ac%e4%bb%bb/','text-button-6005be4'=>'瞭解更多資訊','title-heading-25e790f'=>'負責任的雇主','title-heading-3f5048f'=>'社區','title-heading-833e7d7'=>'我們是','title-heading-e143e59'=>'青年慈善事業','url-button-6005be4'=>'https://h3y8j2unfg-staging.onrocket.site/zh-hant/tag/%e4%bc%81%e6%a5%ad%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e8%b2%ac%e4%bb%bb/']];
